Requirements: 

     - MPS 3.0 (http://www.jetbrains.com/mps/download/)
     - Maven 
     - Ant
     - Ivy

1. Initialize git submodules:

   git submodule init
   git submodule update

2. Compile the required modules and install locally:

   mvn clean install

3. Setup workspace and resolve dependencies:

   ant workspace

4. Launch MPS.

5. Set the path variable "maprules_home" to point to the working dir.

6. Open the project and do a rebuild.

